      "field_id": "Entity/template field identifier. Obtained from get_entity, get_template, save_entity_fields, or save_template_fields.",
      "artifact_id": "Agent memory artifact identifier. Obtained from search_memory_artifacts, create_memory_artifact_draft, get_memory_artifact, or path-based artifact reads.",
